JunctionLocatedAt.description: A directed edge from each junction to its coordinates

RoadUse.description: A directed edge representing vehicles moving from junction A to junction B.

RoadHasJunction.description: A directed edge from each road to all the junctions on that road.

RegionContainsLocation.description: A directed edge from each region to location.

LocationContainsRoad.description: A directed edge from each location to road.

Cardinality.description: An entity that is added to every vertex representing the connectivity of the vertex.

JunctionUse.description: An entity on the junction vertex representing the counts of vehicles moving from junction A to junction B.

junction.description: A road junction represented by a String.

road.description: A road represented by a String.

location.description: A location represented by a String.

anyVertex.description: An String vertex - used for cardinalities

coordinates.description: Coordinates represented by a String in the format 'Eastings,Northings'.

region.description: A region represented by a String.

count.long.description: A long count that must be greater than or equal to 0.

true.description: A simple boolean that must always be true.

date.earliest.description: A Date that when aggregated together will be the earliest date.

date.latest.description: A Date that when aggregated together will be the latest date.
